  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  fontName: Arial
  alwaysReset: 1
  debug: 0
  count: 186
  structSize: 20
  text: 'Sure, it didn''t have the depth of text mesh pro when it came to borders,
    kerning and drop shadows.


    But it could exist *within* the enviornment,
    making the text feel like part of the world instead of just another dry chunk
    of UI.'
