  structSize: 20
  text: "Once upon a time there was a playful unity asset named 'Living Text'. \n\nIt
    was produced by a studio called puddlefish with love and care. But when people
    saw the asset, they were confused about what it did ( and if they should purchase
    it ) so Puddle the puddlefish decided to write a short demonstration of what
    it could do."
